  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Танд <strong>m </strong>x <strong>n</strong> хоёр хэмжээст массив өгөгдөнө. Уг массивыг <strong>r </strong>удаа нар буруу эргүүлнэ.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4 x 5 массивыг эргүүлэхэд.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://hr-challenge-images.s3.amazonaws.com/2517/matrix-rotation.png\" alt=\"matrix-rotation\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Жишээ нь хоёр удаа эргэлт хийхэд.</span></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Start&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; First&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Second</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;1 2 3 4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2&nbsp; 3&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;3&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 6</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">12 1 2 5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1&nbsp; 2&nbsp; 3&nbsp; 6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2&nbsp; 3&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 7</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">11 4 3 6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12&nbsp; 1&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1&nbsp; 2&nbsp; 1&nbsp; 8</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">10 9 8 7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;11 10&nbsp; 9&nbsp; 8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12 11 10&nbsp; 9</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Оролт</strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1 &lt; n, m&lt; 300 ( <strong>min (</strong>m,n)%2=0 )</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">0 &lt; r &lt; 10<sup>9</sup></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">0 &lt; a[i][j] &lt; 10<sup>8</sup> ( i=[1.....n],&nbsp; j=[1.....m] )</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Гаралт</strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>r </strong>эргэлүүлтийн дараах массивыг хэвлэнэ.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Жишээ</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Оролт 1</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4 4 2<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1 2 3 4</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">5 6 7 8</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">9 10 11 12</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">13 14 15 16</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Гаралт 1</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3 4 8 12</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2 11 10 16</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1 7 6 15</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">5 9 13 14</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Тайлбар 1</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;1&nbsp; 2&nbsp; 3&nbsp; 4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2&nbsp; 3&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 8 12</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;5&nbsp; 6&nbsp; 7&nbsp; 8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1&nbsp; 7 11 12&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 11 10 16</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 